Paper: hep-th/9504042

Date: 1995-04-07

Title: Nonlinear Integrable Equations and Nonlinear Fourier Transform

In the paper we study nonlocal functionals whose kernels are homogeneousgeneralized functions. We also use such functionals to solve the Korteweg-deVries , the nonlinear Schr\"odinger and the Davey-Stewartson equations.